      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Antonio Luna was born on October 29, 1866, in Binondo, Manila. He was
    a highly educated Filipino who studied in Spain and earned a degree in pharmacy.
    He was also a scientist and became known for his research in chemistry. At first,
    Luna supported peaceful reforms like other Filipino intellectuals, but after
    witnessing the execution of Filipino patriots and the continued abuse under colonial
    rule, he became more determined to fight for the country\u2019s freedom."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8a89fa14b10d46a99122fd4f73fca9a2, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2140474, guid: 8a89fa14b10d46a99122fd4f73fca9a2, type: 2}
